 <text>
  <front>
   <head>True RESIGNATION.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="couplet">
     <l n="1" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">WHEN Colin's good dame, who long held him a tug,</l>
     <l n="2" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">And defeated his hopes by the help of the jug,</l>
     <l n="3" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">Had taken too  the cheeruping cup,</l>
     <l n="4" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">And  the dose till it laid her quite up;</l>
     <l n="5" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">Colin sent for the doctor: with sorrowful face</l>
     <l n="6" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">He gave him his fee, and he told him her case.</l>
     <l n="7" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">Quoth Galen, I'll do what I can for your wife;</l>
     <l n="8" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">But indeed she's so bad, that I fear, for her life.</l>
     <l n="9" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">In counsel there's safety — e'en send for another;</l>
     <l n="10" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">For if she shou'd die, folks will make a strange pother,</l>
     <l n="11" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">And say that I lost her for want of good skill —</l>
     <l n="12" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">Or of better advice — or, in short, what they will.</l>
     <l n="13" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">Says Colin, your judgment there's none can dispute;</l>
     <l n="14" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">And if physic  cure her — I know  will do't.</l>
     <l n="15" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">But if, after all, she  happen to die,</l>
     <l n="16" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">And they say that  her — I'll swear 'tis a lye:</l>
     <l n="17" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">'Tis the  chief business, whatever ensue;</l>
     <l n="18" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">And  finds fault — I'll be shot — if  do.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
